vote.title: A resolution authorizing the Mayor to appoint an Ad Hoc City Council Canvassing Committee to review the returns of the Saturday, May 6, 2023 general election, and submit a canvass report to the full City Council on Wednesday, May 17, 2023 City Council meeting or at a special called city council meeting - Financing:  No cost consideration to the City
